data.description: Move right into this well-maintained brick/vinyl ranch home on 13.62 acres in Burrell Township built in 1985.  2 bedrooms, 2.5 baths.  This home has an exceptionally large lower level that can be finished into additional bedrooms, family room/game room, etc.  Living room has a beautiful brick, gas fireplace.  Eat-in kitchen has breakfast bar and plenty of cabinet and counter space. French Doors lead out to the side deck from the kitchen.  Tons of storage.  2-car attached garage plus abundance of off-street parking.  Pole building and shed stay.  Pond on the property.
